OL,5,G1320 Midsomer Murders
OL,6,     FThe headmaster of a local school
OL,7,     Fis murdered, his body found pinned
OL,8,     Fto the wall in the manner of his
OL,9,     Fown butterfly collection. The dead
OL,10,     Fman was a member of a mysterious
OL,11,     Finternational club for geniuses,
OL,12,     Fwhich are currently testing the
OL,13,     Fschool's pupils for possible new
OL,14,     Frecruits. Barnaby and Winter
OL,15,     Finvestigate the secretive
OL,16,     Forganisation, which has proven
OL,17,     Fcontroversial in the local area,
OL,18,     Fbut also uncover the possibility
OL,19,     Fof a connection between the
OL,20,     Fkilling and the impact of
OL,21,     Fpesticides on a rare species of
OL,22,     Fbutterfly
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
