OL,5,G1735 The Chase
OL,6,     FBradley Walsh presents as Nathan
OL,7,     Ffrom Hitchin, Olivia originally
OL,8,     Ffrom Guernsey, Michaela from
OL,9,     FLincolnshire and Martyn from
OL,10,     FLondon pit their wits against one
OL,11,     Fof the ruthless Chasers in the
OL,12,     Fhope of winning a potential prize
OL,13,     Fpot worth thousands of pounds.
OL,14,     FThey work as a team and play
OL,15,     Fstrategically to answer general
OL,16,     Fknowledge questions against the
OL,17,     Fclock and race down the game board
OL,18,     Fto the exit without being caught
